|-----------|---------------|---------------------|-------------------|
| **Value Propositions** | Core financial services | 7 | Medium |
| **Customer Segments** | Mid-market businesses | 8 | Low |
| **Revenue Streams** | Subscription + transactions | 6 | High |
| **Key Partnerships** | Regional banks | 5 | High |
| **Key Resources** | Technology platform | 4 | High |
| **Key Activities** | Software development | 6 | Medium |
| **Cost Structure** | 60% technology, 30% personnel | 5 | High |

**Interactive Exercise:** Validate and refine each component

@notes:
- Business model canvas provides structure
- Satisfaction scores reveal pain points
- Priority ratings guide transformation focus
- Technology and partnerships need attention

