    plugins:
      title:
        display: true
        text: "Financial Performance and Targets"

**Current: {{current_revenue}} revenue | Target: {{growth_target}} growth in {{timeline}}**

@notes:
- Financial context drives all decisions
- Growth targets are aggressive but achievable
- Profit margin improvement essential
- Timeline creates urgency for transformation

